        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer899101290" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13581860727447021095">Very cool history, about Europe from an antagonist to European influence. And yet, much as he hates the Franks and loves the Moslems, when waging war he might be fighting either, and at times of peace might be trading with either. Life is never simple, and hasn&apos;t much changed in the last millennium.<br/><br/>Being a translation about 100 years old, you get to see a kind of secondary history attached to the footnotes, a more subtle but equally fascinating bit of reading. <br/><br/>It&apos;s a dense book that doesn&apos;t foll</span>
  <span id="freeText13581860727447021095" style="display:none">Very cool history, about Europe from an antagonist to European influence. And yet, much as he hates the Franks and loves the Moslems, when waging war he might be fighting either, and at times of peace might be trading with either. Life is never simple, and hasn't much changed in the last millennium.<br /><br />Being a translation about 100 years old, you get to see a kind of secondary history attached to the footnotes, a more subtle but equally fascinating bit of reading. <br /><br />It's a dense book that doesn't follow the pattern of a novel. It's more like a conversation with a favorite uncle, who tells some pretty amazing stories.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13581860727447021095" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
