<span id="freeTextContainer8636818749917366297">Written as chatty anecdotes for his patron, Saladin, this is a noble Muslim warrior&apos;s account of encounters with Franks, other Muslim soldiers and leaders, family members, hunting parties, religious experiences and jokes, giving personal insight into the mindset of an elite person in the 11th century middle east.</span>
  <span id="freeText8636818749917366297" style="display:none">Written as chatty anecdotes for his patron, Saladin, this is a noble Muslim warrior's account of encounters with Franks, other Muslim soldiers and leaders, family members, hunting parties, religious experiences and jokes, giving personal insight into the mindset of an elite person in the 11th century middle east.</span>
